HPUX/LVM version 0.01
=========================

This object oriented module extracts the data from several hpux LVM commands
and hashes the results in a single, multi-level hash as documented in the
POD docs included with the source.  It supports remote system data gathering
via ssh or remsh and uses the persistance module to save any data you'd rather
not get again over the net.


INSTALLATION

To install this module type the following:

   perl Makefile.PL
   make
   make test
   make install

DEPENDENCIES

This module requires these other modules and libraries:

  Storable.pm

